Class LoginPacket.LoginDataResponsePacket

  • java.lang.Object

    Enclosing class:
    LoginPacket

    public static class LoginPacket.LoginDataResponsePacket
extends SendOnlyPacket
    A sizable packet. We send this to the client in the final stage of logging in, to send the client all of the data that it needs on initialization to get the player in the game.
